California as an island with nearly flat northern coast and with two place names, C. de Mondouno and C.S. Luc. Blank to the north. The Great Lakes are not shown.
Issued in his: Parallela geographiae veteris et novae, T. I, Paris, 1649.
Reissued in his: Theatre geographique de l'Europe, contenant la division de ses royaumes et provinces, Paris, 1653.
